									<strong>Being a dedicated group of developers we do our very best to provide quailty content by updating Gamer Tagged
										with your suggestions to continue improving upon our users experience.
									</strong>
								</h6>
							</div>
						</div>

					</div>

				</div>
			</div>


		</div>




		<div class="section" id="section2">

			<div class="container">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col s12 m12 l8 offset-l2 card-color card-margin">

						<h1 class="white-text">
							<strong>Gamer Tagged</strong>
						</h1>
						<div class="card card-color-light">
							<div class="card-image card-color-light imageResposive ">
								<img src="assets/images/CaptureGameSpace.PNG">
								<span class="card-title">A new way of gaming</span>
							</div>
							<div class="card-content">

									<h6 id="firstParagraph">
										Experience a new social outlet for gamers and connect with your friends share you digital experiences.
									</h6>
									<h6 id="secondParagraph">With Gamer Tagged you'll be able to connect with like minded individuals, and share your
										achievements from your favorite games both old and new.</h6>
									<h6>
										<strong>You'll have fun updaing your personal library and sharing your adventures with millions of gamers across
											the globe.</strong>
									</h6>

							</div>
						</div>

					</div>
				</div>
			</div>


		</div>

		<div class="section valign-wrapper" id="section3">
